  "unresolvedTextByHash": {
    "09fb8171237bc3fe9d7c3d3b63e74f53523ece0f8a7aacdf2fdea14b0ead3561": "Hello [?]. How's it going?",
    "0cef268c00f77e5b6d22ee9fbcad18f270d087d67a319582d4b38f701cf52634": "How goes it [?]?",
    "18cbcae0ce6e77c0af1c9c268d222eefbfb7b6c3354f1352654cd37ff6a2be91": "This is good news indeed, [?]. That should stop anyone from entering for another thousand years.",
    "19731fff36acad142dba28eff81ec44fa3992ef2770f351f752cd6efa9f4574a": "I am well [?], yourself?",
    "1a3ec7b2f985da74cb0967d3d8f954f722b118d5530e2e1ae5285e65128c43cd": "Right, [?], talk to Lord Amlodd when you are ready. Good luck.",
    "1adf99d7a298ac27d9265b8b1b694b5372f47c322f12b380bf0f11de50138366": "Ah [?], glad to see you made it. Welcome to Lletya, home to the Elven Resistance.",
    "252881af3abf870220971b658cb6168e46ab54418db98552df836667a0283a9c": "Are you the human by the name [?]?",
    "30db138867c15183f680cc571a6d9aedb11d188f8df38fc7530fa0a16eae9b69": "[?], you have returned. Did you discover anything in the Grand Library?",
    "32fdfec37b8a32cf6fc6d62087b15514886132e674153e48d3b62add4ef2e109": "[?], myself and Baxtorian will continue to work on deciphering these clues. While we do, it would be of great help if you could find Lord Amlodd and Lady Trahaearn for us.",
    "4b1badaf2db10793cdea0d51605a8ec467ac0576120e8c90781cf18068a86e42": "Thank you for agreeing to help us, [?]. We owe a lot to you, even if some of us don't show it very well.",
    "50ae823cd9e2c969e9fe66aa91ab1bbf073272a7129a802aed10c91f84b713ba": "Right, thanks to [?], we should now have everything we need to enter the crystal seed containing Prifddinas.",
    "58f684e41077d8ebfd1b257c68328ac32dee190832c7b6dbf1bb1f4b004f9244": "Hello there [?], glad to see you made it here okay.",
    "6807397d5934164dd7de98635038c4ec8b2079b72314e2456d9434946e2e2b47": "Hello [?], how's the potion going?",
    "6a23255b8a61f1c4c06d445404f43c9e20c560846db7f8bf6807f5cb962a44b4": "Welcome back [?]. While you were gone, I filled Baxtorian in on everything that has happened. I also took the liberty of calling the others here, so that we can discuss our next move.",
    "6c30587e67ebe7d94d5788fa406b013b6ec11b77cfd7537c04d483e42469c154": "[?], you've been to Baxtorian Falls multiple times. You're the best person to take the lead on this.",
    "8a98d84c8ceb6e417528323a6aa14478834db289392b6a135402535560cd01a5": "If it's any consolation, [?] moved her remains here, to be closer to you.",
    "93b16c511e12be9788b6932a897d39a6f4db34e59677b66a81f6f7b9741b7894": "So you managed to break all of Seren's seals? Very impressive [?]. Now tell us, this memory, what was it?",
    "9596bc68cc3051f6b31bfad8ebfbaba406b0868800104ac8e5aa8c66f905df9c": "Until next time, [?].",
    "a8ff11ede1a19c7be7f82e55702436c68bca0df0c40ab5414966e05be21111b3": "[?] here has an old crystal sample, we need you to make a replacement for it.",
    "c17c49d4f0c530d323c22ea38ce9f3623fbcea1404c2cab1c362c7e8617b9ddc": "Great work! Stick with it [?].",
    "c9a4af895708ea7e1c22683277f57ea7536035009c4ca74234061562055dbf0f": "Okay, thank you all for joining us. In case you weren't aware, [?] here has returned from the Grand Library with some news for us.",
    "ce771a08050c600a2cbe78c9c35a5976bf4460e521df730af0bfc1181fb485e5": "I'd like to accompany you on this one [?], it might be useful to have an elf with you.",
    "d4c971c4d31f9d9533d96f9be4ce0d5f954823e8187b6fb4103344ee1abee7b5": "[?], what is the latest news?",
    "d9337be30a9e462cc8dc5872647fd90a3584e13247989040e1688709cc7403bc": "Then I propose that [?] be the one sent into the crystal. Anyone disagree?",
    "de7133beeea8a3f034964a7c1af24cb8e05c64ec8a0b15e0c49911703031538a": "Ah [?], there you are. We thought it best to let you rest for a bit after everything that happened earlier.",
    "df1ae022f1a0c2a7399e5fc4a59c6753be11bad82ccf1878e9710479cbe59297": "Indeed we do. Baxtorian's knowledge allowed [?] to reunite us with Lord Amlodd and Lady Trahaearn. It was the Amlodd clan that created those defences, Lord Amlodd can overcome them for us.",
    "df21c54721999b4aa8530965594ec47769b0c6b5cfa958ca8c6a137a102f2a51": "Now, while freeing [?] and Elena from the Iorwerth camp, we were confronted by Lord Iorwerth. He could have killed us all, but he let us go.",
    "ee633434ec53b7a3482cb679d25ab65fb2938cdccc545fbd14f3db56b8a3d42a": "Very well, I will teleport us back to Lletya. You'll have to make your own way back I'm afraid, [?].",
    "f14973a122d888bf9525aa58188c8096cd28a528a593e662f526c8a24a177790": "Good luck in the library, [?]. We're all counting on you. Speak to Lord Amlodd when you're ready."
  }
}